heading: Lost Keep Dungeon Guide
content: Lost Keep does not contain any super dangerous monsters, but has a confusing layout that can lead to a great deal of backtracking. As a currently possible , it is not great for farming mostly due to the presence of ultra-tanky Animus Carriers. The Resurrected Malice is an easy boss to defeat, only having one annoying attack where it knocks you back if you are in melee range. This dungeon unlocks the , a decent defensive aspect for all classes. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
